---
import UnitOfCompetencyList from './UnitOfCompetencyList.astro';
---

<div class="space-y-12">
  <section>
    <h3 class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-ink-3);">
      Five-unit course with a superseded-codes note (canonical)
    </h3>
    <p
      class="t-body mt-2"
      style="color: var(--color-ink-2); font-size: 14px; max-width: 70ch;"
    >
      The five NSW Owner Builder units, with the regulator's note that prior
      code versions are also accepted.
    </p>
    <div
      class="mt-3 px-6 py-6"
      style="border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); background: var(--color-bg);"
    >
      <UnitOfCompetencyList
        heading="What will you learn?"
        units={[
          { code: 'CPCCWHS2001', title: 'Apply WHS requirements, policies and procedures in the construction industry' },
          { code: 'CPCCOM2001', title: 'Read and interpret plans and specifications' },
          { code: 'CPCCCM1011', title: 'Undertake basic estimation and costing' },
          { code: 'CPCCOM1013', title: 'Plan and organise work' },
          { code: 'CPCCOM1014', title: 'Conduct workplace communication' },
        ]}
        supersededNote="Older versions (CPCCOHS2001A, CPCCCM2001A, CPCCCM1011A, CPCCCM1013A, CPCCCM1014A) are also accepted if you completed them previously."
        caption="Units verified against Building Commission NSW on 28 April 2026."
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h3 class="t-label" style="color: var(--color-ink-3);">
      Single-unit course with elements and delivery
    </h3>
    <p
      class="t-body mt-2"
      style="color: var(--color-ink-2); font-size: 14px; max-width: 70ch;"
    >
      A one-unit White Card course — the optional <code>elements</code> and
      <code>delivery</code> fields render as a mono caps meta line.
    </p>
    <div
      class="mt-3 px-6 py-6"
      style="border: 1px solid var(--color-rule); background: var(--color-bg);"
    >
      <UnitOfCompetencyList
        heading="Unit of competency"
        units={[
          {
            code: 'CPCWHS1001',
            title: 'Prepare to work safely in the construction industry',
            elements: 4,
            delivery: 'Online (Zoom)',
          },
        ]}
        caption="Unit details verified against training.gov.au in April 2026."
      />
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
